data.text:
The minimum age is usually 18 years-old but it might vary based on the event. It also possible that the age cap varies for girls and boys. We recommend you double-check before visiting Privilege or purchasing your tickets

Please have a valid ID, passport or driver license when you attend the venue. If you hold a piece of ID (other than passport) from a non-western country you might want to use your passport instead to make sure it is recognised and deemed legit by the bouncers.

Similar questions: What is the age requirement to enter Privilege? Am I old enough to enter Privilege? What is the age limit for entry into Privilege? How old do you have to be to enter Privilege?

There are 3 form of ID's that will guarantee you entry into Privilege and are as follows:

National ID card

Driving License

Passport

Photocopies or screenshots of the above might be accepted but remains at the discretion of the bouncers.

Similar questions: Do they accept passport at Privilege? Do I need an ID to enter Privilege? Do they check IDs at Privilege? Can I enter with a driving license at Privilege?

Tickets can be purchased at the door (On the day), unless the event is sold out or capped. We recommend to buy your tickets online and in advance to avoid any disappointment so you are guaranteed entry. Generally the entrance fee (cover charge) is higher at the door and on weekends.

Here is a typical entry price range you can expect: 20€ to 50€

Similar questions: Where do I get tickets to get in Privilege? Can I buy ticket at the door at Privilege? Can I buy online tickets to enter Privilege? Do they sell tickets at the door at Privilege?

Privilege's dress code is Casual (No sportswear). It is recommended to abide by this dress code to maximise your chances of entering the venue. In case you need to drop a bag or any other item of clothing the venues has a PAID cloakroom, price usually vary from 2USD to 5USD per item, dress light to save and skip the cloakroom queue. The cloakroom item should be no bigger than a rucksack or a handbag. Large suitcase or trekking backpack will not be accepted.

We strive to reply all messages under 24 hours.
